claim.claim-text:
An electronic distance meter (10) comprising:
an optical unit (12) which emits light (Pm) to a target object (12) and receives the light (Pr) reflected by the target object with a light receiving element (23);
a measuring unit (13) which calculates a length of round-trip time taken for the light to reciprocatively travel to the target object and measures a distance to the target object according to the round-trip time of the received light;
a light receiving system (19) which receives and condenses the light reflected by the target object;
an optical guide which guides the light condensed by the light receiving element to the light receiving system, including a multi-mode graded index fiber (26) and a multi-mode step index fiber (27) coupled with each other.
